show.description: Devraj thought he had buried Arjun forever but ghosts don’t stay dead for long. Fueled by loss and betrayal, Arjun returns to take down the kingdom that turned its back on him. Shehzaada is a dark, thrilling ride through vengeance, power, and redemption. Watch Now !
